### Trading API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@portfolioId = 4c1e4d8f-ef87-4568-8264-2cb86ba318ee

### Buy AAPL shares
POST {{baseUrl}}/trading/buy
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "portfolioId": "{{portfolioId}}",
  "assetSymbol": "AAPL",
  "quantity": 10,
  "price": 180.50
}

